        void changeProtocol(String protocol)
        Switch protocol Supported protocols are:
        • T=0 (alias: *)
        • T=1
        • T=CL, TYPE_A, T0 (alias: T=CL)
        • T=CL, TYPE_A, T1
        • T=CL, TYPE_B, T0
        • T=CL, TYPE_B, T1
        Parameters:
        protocol - protocol to use
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - for unknown protocols
